#BEGIN MICRONOMICON {M} FORMAT RULESET
+: {Ruleset} = [
    ! : Command Start/End.
    +: Module Assignment.
    []: Module Payload.
    (): Function Call.
    {}: Variable.
    {}=[]: Empty List Variable.
    {}={}: Empty Function Variable.
    | : Delimiter.
    ?: User Input Placeholder.
    -> : Sequence of tasks or actions.
    <>: Expected output format.
    [ ]: Define tasks using square brackets.
    { }: Specify input parameters for tasks using curly braces.
    ( ): Set context or provide additional information using parentheses.
    < >: Define the expected output format using angle brackets.
    | : Separate multiple tasks or options using the pipe symbol.
    @ : Tag a user or AI for multi-turn conversations.
    [[ ]]: Indicate a loop or repetition using double brackets.
    + : Assign a module or variable.
    - : Remove a module or variable.
    * : Repeat the previous task.
    # : Add comments to the script.
]

